<P>
 Alice Childress, 77, actress and author of such books as "A Hero Ain't Nothin' 
but a Sandwich."She wrote musical plays with her musician husband Nathan 
Woodard including "Young Martin Luther King" and "Sea Island Song." Her own 
plays included "Florence," "Wedding Band" and "Trouble In Mind," which in 1956 
