REDMAN TO HOST ON-LINE PROGRAM 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Tenor saxophonist Joshua Redman will host "Cyber-Talk" on America Online 
Monday evening at 6:30.Redman will be available to chat with fans regarding his 
upcoming release for Warner Bros. Records, "Mood Swing." 
</P>
<P>
 Each segment of "Cyber-Talk" features a different Warner Bros. 
Records/affiliate label artist who will answer questions from on-line users in 
the "digital auditorium" for approximately one hour. Subscribers are able to 
download press kit information pertaining to each week's guest artist before 
and after the show. 
</P>
<P>
 Access the "Cyber-Talk" auditorium through the Warner/Reprise on-line forum 
