 Week-ago: Albums: 11.0 Singles: 2.2 
</P>
<P>
 Year-ago: Albums: 10.5 Singles: 2.7 Hits Magazine Tip of the Week 
</P>
<P>
 As Bertelsmann Music Group continues its long search for a North American CEO 
to oversee its film, cable and music divisions, which include the RCA, Zoo and 
Imago record labels, industry speculation is increasing over the future role of 
current RCA President Joe Galante. Galante, who just signed a new BMG contract, 
