<P>
 UCLA hospital -- In an article in Sunday's editions, the UCLA Medical School 
was incorrectly included among a group of elite teaching hospitals responding 
to changes in health care. The article should have named UCLA Medical Center, a 
private Los Angeles hospital closely affiliated with the medical school. 
